Exceptional Handling : 

to handle runtime errors so that normal flow of application can be maintained 





statement1;
statement2;
statement3;
statement4;
statement5;   //exception occurs
statement6;
statement7;
statement8;
statement9;
statement10;



Two Types Of Exception :

1> Checked Exception
2> Unchecked Exception



								Throwable
									|
			---------------------------------------------------------
			|														|
		CheckedException                                        Exception
		|                                                           |
		|-IOException                                           RuntimeTime(Unchecked Exception)
		|-SQL													|
		|-ClassNotFound											|-Arithmetic
																|-NullPointer
																|-NumberFormat
																|-ArrayIndexOutOfBound
			                                                         
		try {
				//if exception occurs, then it will go to catch block
		}
		catch						   